com.binance4j.market.trade

Class AggTradeRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.binance4j.core.request.Request
      • com.binance4j.market.trade.AggTradeRequest

  • public class AggTradeRequest
extends com.binance4j.core.request.Request
    A request to get compressed, aggregate trades. Trades that fill at the time, from the same order, with the same price will have the quantity aggregated.
